  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK277">
<l>puṟaṅkuṉṟi kaṇṭaṉaiya rēṉu makamkuṉṟi</l>
<l>mūkkiṟ kariyā ruṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The world) contains persons whose outside appears (as fair) as the (red) berry of the Abrus, but whose inside is as black as the nose of that berry.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
